feat(D2): add EVM fee translation for KakarotAdapter

- Add estimate_evm_fee() to KakarotAdapter Cairo contract
  Returns (protocol_fee, gas_premium, total_fee) given amount and EVM gas used
- Add estimateEvmFee() to StarkPrivacyClient SDK
  Pure computation: protocol fee (0.1% BPS) + gas premium (gas * factor / 10000)
- Gas price factor is admin-configurable via set_gas_price_factor()
